paragraphs.title: Original VE Graph
paragraphs.text:
import java.sql.Date
import java.time.LocalDate

import edu.drexel.cs.dbgroup.portal._
import edu.drexel.cs.dbgroup.portal.representations.VEGraph
import org.apache.spark.graphx._
import org.apache.spark.rdd.RDD
import org.apache.spark.storage.StorageLevel
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.{StructField, _}
import org.apache.spark.sql.Row
import edu.drexel.cs.dbgroup.portal.ProgramContext

ProgramContext.setContext(sc)

val vschema = StructType(
  StructField("VID", LongType, false) ::
  StructField("Start", DateType, false) ::
  StructField("End", DateType, false) ::
  StructField("Name", StringType, false) :: Nil
)

val eschema = StructType(
  StructField("EID", LongType, false) ::
  StructField("SrcId", LongType, false) ::
  StructField("DstId", LongType, false) ::
  StructField("Start", DateType, false) ::
  StructField("End", DateType, false) ::
  StructField("Value", StringType, false) :: Nil
)

val verticesToDf = (vertices: RDD[(VertexId, (Interval, String))]) => sqlContext.createDataFrame(vertices.map{ case (vid, (interval, name)) => Row(vid, Date.valueOf(interval.start), Date.valueOf(interval.end), name)},vschema)
val edgesToDf = (edges: RDD[TEdge[String]]) => sqlContext.createDataFrame(edges.map{edge => Row(edge.eId, edge.srcId, edge.dstId, Date.valueOf(edge.interval.start), Date.valueOf(edge.interval.end), edge.attr)},eschema)

val users: RDD[(VertexId, (Interval, String))] = sc.parallelize(Array(
  (1L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Bob")),
  (2L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Barbara")),
  (3L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2015-01-01")), "Donald")),
  (4L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2011-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Debbie")),
  (5L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Edward"))
))

val friendships: RDD[(TEdge[String])] = sc.parallelize(Array(
  TEdge[String](1L, 1L, 2L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Friend"),
  TEdge[String](2L, 2L, 3L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Friend"),
  TEdge[String](3L, 3L, 4L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2011-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01")), "Friend"),
  TEdge[String](4L, 4L, 5L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Friend"),
  TEdge[String](5L, 2L, 5L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Friend")
))

val VEG = VEGraph.fromRDDs(users,friendships, "Default", StorageLevel.MEMORY_ONLY_SER)

paragraphs.text:
val sliceInterval = Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"))
val slicedVEG = VEG.slice(sliceInterval)

paragraphs.title: Vertex and Edge Map
paragraphs.text:
val vmapped = VEG.vmap((vid, interval, name) => s"${name} the friendly node", "DefaultName")
val emapped = vmapped.emap(tedge => s"Best${tedge.attr}")

val eSelectFunction = (trip: TEdgeTriplet[String, String]) => trip.srcId == 2
val esubgraph = VEG.esubgraph(eSelectFunction, TripletFields.None)

paragraphs.title: Temporal Node Creation
paragraphs.text:
val resolution5years = Resolution.between(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2015-01-01"))
val existsIn5Years = VEG.createTemporalNodes(new TimeSpec(resolution5years), Exists(), Exists(), (name1, name2) => name1, (type1, type2) => type1)

paragraphs.title: Structural Node Creation
paragraphs.text:
val vertexAggregationFunction = (name1: String, name2: String) => name1
val vertexGroupByFunction = (vid: VertexId, name: String) => name.head.toString.hashCode.toLong
val groupByFirstLetter = VEG.createAttributeNodes(vertexAggregationFunction)(vertexGroupByFunction)

paragraphs.title: Union, Intersection, and Difference
paragraphs.text:
val users1: RDD[(VertexId, (Interval, String))] = sc.parallelize(Array(
  (1L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Bob")),
  (2L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Barbara")),
  (3L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2015-01-01")), "Clyde"))
))

val friendships1: RDD[(TEdge[String])] = sc.parallelize(Array(
  TEdge[String](1L, 1L, 2L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Friend"),
  TEdge[String](2L, 2L, 3L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Friend")
))

val VEG1 = VEGraph.fromRDDs(users1,friendships1, "Default", StorageLevel.MEMORY_ONLY_SER)

val users2: RDD[(VertexId, (Interval, String))] = sc.parallelize(Array(
  (1L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2016-01-01")), "Bob")),
  (2L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Barbara")),
  (4L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2011-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Debbie")),
  (5L, (Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Edward"))
))

val friendships2: RDD[(TEdge[String])] = sc.parallelize(Array(
  TEdge[String](1L, 1L, 2L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2010-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2016-01-01")), "Friend"),
  TEdge[String](4L, 4L, 5L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2014-01-01")), "Friend"),
  TEdge[String](5L, 2L, 5L, Interval(LocalDate.parse("2012-01-01"), LocalDate.parse("2013-01-01")), "Friend")
))

val VEG2 = VEGraph.fromRDDs(users2,friendships2, "Default", StorageLevel.MEMORY_ONLY_SER)

val unionVEG = VEG1.union(VEG2, (name1, name2) => name1, (type1, type2) => type1)

val intersectionVEG = VEG1.intersection(VEG2, (name1, name2) => name1, (type1, type2) => type1)

val differenceVEG = VEG1.difference(VEG2)
